column4: Hey, could someone help me. Azureus won't start and I miss it :) there is a problem with Java.. here is the error.. http://paste.ubuntu-nl.org/52527/
You can use a different bittorrent client (I like Deluge), but that's only a temporary fix to your problem.
You could try reinstalling the Java packages and the Azureus package, for starters.
